--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8ef659fb6f36bdb429daea399a91329e, type: 3}
  m_Name: DD_NPC01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueLines:
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: Hmm? What are visitors doing here at a time like this?
  - speakerName: HUGO
    text: "Name\u2019s Hugo. I\u2019m looking for the shrines within the Twin Mountains
      nearby. I hear your tribe frequents the area, but I must ask\u2026 is it just
      you here?"
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: The shrine, huh? I must want you, that place is now nothing but the spawn
      of our demise.
  - speakerName: HUGO
    text: Demise?
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: We used to visit there for prayers so that our hunting sessions would be
      fruitful.
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: Recently, however, the shrine has fallen ill. A virus that is slowly killing
      off all life in Thornden, including us.
  - speakerName: TENET
    text: My master! Perhaps that is why that wolf looked to be in pain!
  - speakerName: ' SOLEMN RESIDENT '
    text: Who are you supposed to be?
  - speakerName: TENET
    text: You may call me Tenet. We seek answers to my existence at your shrine.
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: "I\u2019ll be. A living spirit\u2026 \r\nPerhaps you may live long enough
      to outlast the virus\u2026\r"
  - speakerName: TENET
    text: My master and I are more than capable of handling anything! If you wish,
      we can also deal with this virus ourselves!
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: "We appreciate the help, but I must warn you\u2026"
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: Should either of you fall, the other will become nothing more than a husk.
  - speakerName: TENET
    text: Not to worry, resident! My master has faced death a number of times.
  - speakerName: SOLEMN RESIDENT
    text: "Even so\u2026 nevermind. Wish you the best of luck out there."
  - speakerName: TENET
    text: "Let\u2019s get a move on, master!"
  - speakerName: HUGO
    text: "\u2026"
  - speakerName: TENET
    text: Master?
